| Feature               | Normal LB (L4)     | Application LB (L7)               |
| --------------------- | ------------------ | --------------------------------- |
| OSI Layer             | Layer 4            | Layer 7                           |
| Routing Based On      | IP + Port          | URL, Hostname, Headers, Cookies   |
| Protocols             | TCP/UDP            | HTTP/HTTPS/WebSocket              |
| SSL Termination       | ❌ No               | ✅ Yes                             |
| Content-Based Routing | ❌ No               | ✅ Yes                             |
| Best Use              | Non-HTTP workloads | Web apps & APIs                   |
| Performance           | Very high          | Slightly lower (more intelligent) |
